All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
CarShape
A car made up of 2D Shapes
CompositeShape
CompositeShape is an interface that defines a number of operations that the shapes must carry out
ShapeDisplayer
The main application that layouts all the components
ShapeIcon
A ShapeIcon takes a CompositeShape and turns it into an Icon for the buttons
ShapePanel
A ShapePanel is a JPanel that stores a list of CompositeShapes and the mousePoint of a user when they click
SmileyFace
A SmileyFace is a CompositeShape made of ellipses and a rectangle to form an emoji like graphic
SnowMan
A SnowMan is a CompositeShape made of two ellipses stacked on top of each other
